                            <comment id="17147416" author="dongjoon" created="Sun, 28 Jun 2020 18:54:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I also verified that this is a long standing bug at 1.6.3 ~ 3.0.0 and Apache Hive 2.3.7 has no problem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
hive&amp;gt; SELECT SUBSTRING(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;abc&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, -1207959552, -1207959552);
OK
Time taken: 4.291 seconds, Fetched: 1 row(s)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17147417" author="dongjoon" created="Sun, 28 Jun 2020 18:56:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Although this might be a rare case, but I raise this issue as a Blocker issue because this is a correctness issue .&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
